illones unidades IM q2–4 semanas","guid":"VUHbFn1f47BTrRM6liYFDA","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"• Función renal normal: Vida media 0.5 hr","guid":"J-kfucDftVhQoaoX2d3tNw","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"• ESRD: Vida media 6-20 hr","guid":"H8llSi2Dlcuedj2WE7k27g","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"57","text":"• Peso corporal y depuración\\Nde creatinina (CrCl):","guid":"EMrN97NkHbEEBBpMkeG6GQ","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"• Dosis (función renal normal): 0.5-4 millones U IV q4h","guid":"ToCiYI3tBPOfqYd3Pl2Oqg","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"• CrCl >50-90: 0.5-4 millones U q4h","guid":"RRSahyRpwmmOn8co0L_ffQ","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"• CrCl 10-50: 0.5-4 millones U q8h","guid":"wkR6cTrpvmQ5Lil9hec-uA","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"61","text":"• CrCl <10: 0.5-4 millones U q12h","guid":"T40V6bjxJ-adxay6qCJDvw","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"61","text":"• HD: 0.5-4 millones U q12h (una dosis en día de diálisis AD)","guid":"ynLpZc0chPAwcVUn5-E48w","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"61","text":"• CAPD: 0.5-4 millones U q12h","guid":"r6x7y3d4qifVOwOZx0-lgA","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"61","text":"• CRRT: 1-4 millones U q6-8h","guid":"Cq8ZZCwuimgwH_Au-n1A3Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"57","text":"Ajuste Hepático: Ninguno","guid":"cXsjOZlX-acuHxondUTDuw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"0","text":"2. Espectro de\\Nactividad:","guid":"AawS24P7MQrSyaOvVNHdJA","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"• Cocos gram\\N(+):","guid":"iShyee2s-gAJRneqCmuE2g","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"• No productores de penicilinasa → estafilococos (raro), estreptococos β-hemolíticos\\N(grupos A, B, C, G), estreptococos viridans susceptibles, estreptococos grupo D.","guid":"TS0tVHmjVoJy1fVaDnNkUg","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"71","text":"• Streptococcus pneumoniae susceptible (↑ resistencia).","guid":"8RXHaRyuNPCj4HQYsAAOTA","children":[]}]},{"id":